		<title>Kayli's Banners</title>
		<style>
			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			body {
				font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
				background: repeating-linear-gradient(
					90deg,
					#f8f9fa,
					#f8f9fa 20px,
					#f1f3f4 20px,
					#f1f3f4 40px
